            <thetext>IS:

the qx.Mobile Menu remembers the previous selected item, no matter if logic uses &quot;setSelectedIndex(null)&quot; to reset the selection. This is because, the render method is only used on, when user taps on list, but not if the selectedIndex was changed.

SHOULD:

The menu should be able to forget its previous selection. The render() method should called in _applySelectedIndex()</thetext>
